Behold, I am sending you out as sheep in the midst of wolves, so be wise as serpents and innocent as doves."

A herd of sheep is a symbol of the masses, the mindless crowd, those that follow wherever the majority is guided.  The wolf represents the cunning predator that preys on the weak. 

The sheep hangs lifeless in mid-leap above "Bloodbath Project" and under it reads: "Cousins of Death". Stop counting sheep and don't sleep on us.

name: Augustine Backpack (Black)
description:
Rucksack style back pack. Built with Ballistic nylon and PU leather in a modernized yet classic, militant yet elegant type of silhouette. Its a durable bag that demands attention while being stealthy. 

Details & Specs:

Featuring outer shell pockets, side zippered flap pockets, full leather back area and sides, black gunmetal buckles and zipper pulls, the top flap opens the main compartment, exhibiting the riveted rucksack opening with drawcord, but the flap also serves as a pocket for your music device complete with riveted opening for your headphones.  Inside also has a laptop sleeve with velcro closure and a zippered pocket.
